    create_mode="Default")

    stream_analytics_job_name=azurerm_stream_analytics_job["example"]["name"],
    resource_group_name=azurerm_stream_analytics_job["example"]["resource_group_name"],
    server=example_sql_server.fully_qualified_domain_name,
